'''Nicholas "Nicky" Read''' is an actor who played the [[Ewok]] [[Nicki]] in [[Star Wars: Episode VI Return of the Jedi|''Star Wars'': Episode VI ''Return of the Jedi'']]. He was credited as '''Nicki Reade''' in the film.

Read also appeared in such films as ''Labyrinth'' and ''Without Work: The Drive Away''.

